{
    "name": "Recruit",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>During Combat</b> The warrior prefers melee combat and working with other soldiers. He uses alchemist\u2019s fire against targets resistant to weapon damage."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "Filled with bluster and swagger, a recruit lacks the discipline of an experienced soldier and can quickly lose resolve if he finds himself in over his head. A recruit works best in a large group under a strong leader who can keep all the soldiers in line and working together.<br/><br/>Left to his own devices, a recruit becomes bored and looks for entertainments such as drinking and gambling to pass the time."
        }
    ],
